	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-172817926" class="story-title"> <a   href="//news.slashdot.org/story/24/01/25/0045235/doomsday-clock-stays-at-90-seconds-to-midnight">Doomsday Clock Stays at 90 Seconds To Midnight</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-68017445"  title="External link - https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-68017445" target="_blank"> (bbc.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
